{"tid":1212170,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Please，明天鐵路已經 confirm 左會有好多人，請大家唔好塞隧道!","createTime":"2019-06-12T17:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T18:16:41.000Z","uid":84497,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fe9a988ef49a03f9b714b78601bfd9f13b3f9cd1","tid":1212170,"uid":84497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:33:53.000Z","msg":"已知明早地鐵會癱瘓，但好多人要返工架，請大家千萬千萬千萬不要係各大隧道玩死火! 我真係會返唔到工架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地玩下街道好了，街有咁多條，你塞呢條，我地兜下路都還可以去到要去既地方，但隧道比起馬路更為重要，我平時8點頭架巴士轉滿人過隧道架，大家千萬千萬不要死火! 會有成千上萬人返唔到工的! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n返唔到工既話，香港會亂架!<br />\n<br />\n大家記住睇睇地圖先，睇清楚香港有邊各大新界出九龍，九龍過海既隧道，真係跪求大家呢幾日唔好死火係隧道中心呀!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跪求大家了!"},{"pid":"cfb5ad6c8d4bf926e3db89195f849124ed26f56c","tid":1212170,"uid":258973,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:36:08.000Z","msg":"我個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac5c1c82d1ff4e5ecbb343f53317ee6961f9644","tid":1212170,"uid":84497,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:55:22.000Z","msg":"各位車主高抬貴手!"},{"pid":"9c4555af2a42e57aa70740ace0b1c48e0c142239","tid":1212170,"uid":245101,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:14:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26b2c17b26f2f33406a892b793d803be9a64be37","tid":1212170,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:16:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ww